emuInput.TitMainTitle: Seven men and six women, members of Centre Avenue YMCA roller skating club, posed in line in Y gymnasium
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 15, 1945, pg. 17, reads: "Skate Demons - All set for a dash around the big Centre Avenue YMCA gym are members of the roller skating club, which will resume activities Sept. 22.  William Strother is club advisor and skate master.  Matinee and evening programs will be featured. - Harris Photo."
